{
  "stem": "22582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the evening, they gave us another blanket.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody had their own blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were a lot of-- lot of flies and lot of-- first time that I really got infested.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- for liquidation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whenever we go-- we went at that time, they were liquidating, because they were pushing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't-- they had all the-- the army was coming closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians were coming closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were going east-- west, all the time west.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were liquidating the camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when you came into camps, they didn't have where to put you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From Ohrdruf they sent us walking to Buchenwald, which was not too far.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember, I went through Weimar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were bombarding the city, the Allied planes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the way, there were, like bombs were coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then Germans were shooting a prisoner, you know, one of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a woman who saw what was going, she started from the window-- because we're going through a town-- and she was yelling and crying when she saw that they were shooting the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was really something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they were shooting a prisoner in Weimar when we were passing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know for what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing for us, I mean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was yelling, crying, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the bombs were falling, like-- like it there be altogether, as I remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we came to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Buchenwald was about 12 kilometers from Weimar.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
